About
Fusion Telecommunications International, Inc is located at the address 420 Lexington Ave Rm 1718 in New York, New York 10170.  They can be contacted via phone at (212) 201-2400 for pricing, hours and directions.  Fusion Telecommunications International, Inc has an annual sales volume of 20M – 49,999,999.  .For more information contact Ellon  Peterkin, Administrator or  go to www.fusiontel.comFusion Telecommunications International, Inc provides Phone & Internet, Digital Network, Data Communication Systems to it's customers.  For maps and directions to Fusion Telecommunications International, Inc view the map to the right.  For reviews of Fusion Telecommunications International, Inc see below.









